I '''Petr Nečas''' (mibait 19 Noviembre 1964; {{IPA-cs|ˈpɛtr̩ ˈnɛtʃas}}) metung yang [[Pun Ministru ning Republika ning Tseka]] ampong pekapun ning [[Civic Democratic Party (Czech Republic)|Civic Democratic Party]]. Sinumpa ya anyang 28 Junio 2010.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ceskenoviny.cz/news/zpravy/klaus-names-necas-new-czech-prime-minister/497007|title=Klaus names Necas new Czech prime minister|date=28 June 2010|work=České Noviny ([[ČTK|Czech Press Agency]])|accessdate=3 July 2010}}</ref> 

Migdimitir ya anyang 17 Junio 2013, kaybat ning kimut da reng pulis, nung nu merakap ya ing kayang pekapun ning tanggapan (''chief of office''), i Jana Nagyová.[3]

